<li id='fn-493041-56'> Saesam Lee, “Japan takes economic retaliation against Korea for forced labor ruling,” <em>The Dong-a Ilbo</em>, July 2, 2019, available at <a href="https://www.donga.com/en/article/all/20190702/1777520/1/Japan-takes-economic-retaliation-against-Korea-for-forced-labor-ruling">https://www.donga.com/en/article/all/20190702/1777520/1/Japan-takes-economic-retaliation-against-Korea-for-forced-labor-ruling</a>. <span class='footnotereverse'><a href='#fnref-493041-56'>&#8617;</a></span></li>
